  "title": "Crispy Bitter Tagliatelle Stir-fry",
  "description": "A crunchy Argentinian dish featuring bitter tagliatelle stir-fried with a dash of friendliness and crispy texture for a solo dinner option.",
  "cuisine": "Argentinean",
