      "amount": "1 tsp"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add minced garlic and sauté until fragrant, about 2 minutes.",
    "Add roasted bell peppers and stir to combine with the garlic.",
    "Add tagliatelle to the skillet and toss well with the vegetables.",
    "Drizzle balsamic vinegar on top of the mixture and season with salt and black pepper.",
    "Stir in red chili flakes if desired, and cook for an additional minute until everything is heated through and crispy.",
    "Serve hot as a solo dinner option."
